  "content": "<p data-pid=\"aPDsr92Z\">之前发过一个想法，里面的代码还可以用，这里补上详细的教程。</p><p data-pid=\"Z5fasg80\"><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/pin/1090633274971422720\" class=\"internal\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"visible\">zhihu.com/pin/109063327</span><span class=\"invisible\">4971422720</span><span class=\"ellipsis\"></span></a></p><p data-pid=\"g-s2N0RV\">阅读须知：本文仅针对已经在Ankidroid上使用TTS的读者，满足指定特定字段文字转语音而非整张卡片转语音的需求。</p><hr/><h2>首先是安卓端的教程</h2><p data-pid=\"wVqdm1TQ\">打开 Ankidroid 2.9 的用户手册</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//docs.ankidroid.org/manual.html\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-00fd4cdbbf76cfb81308c88244438ca2_120x160.jpg\" data-image-width=\"240\" data-image-height=\"320\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">AnkiDroid 2.9 User Manual</a><p data-pid=\"5ijfuIk-\">Ctrl + F，搜索 TTS</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6314ad6afad53538b26560d2823bf449_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1227\" data-rawheight=\"235\" data-original-token=\"v2-6a409d896519a88783a148d06afe1a2b\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1227\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6314ad6afad53538b26560d2823bf449_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"06AZrlS4\">找到对应的手册章节</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4cdd97ac465dbacfe8fd7cef9b79a2ac_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1497\" data-rawheight=\"829\" data-original-token=\"v2-c38da6e585d85f34f9e5ebab71f73265\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1497\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4cdd97ac465dbacfe8fd7cef9b79a2ac_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"PDZ-o8xs\">阅读手册，对照自己使用的模板，我用的是划词助手Antimoon模板</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fe62fb4173c255b3550a762d0031993d_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"814\" data-rawheight=\"736\" data-original-token=\"v2-62dbc6373263c89697035243e6fa8b8f\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"814\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-fe62fb4173c255b3550a762d0031993d_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"tQkkgQTy\">编写满足自己需求的代码，我想要在卡片正面播放我的英文例句，于是在正面将 {{例句}} 改写成</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-html\">\t<span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">tts</span> <span class=\"na\">service</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;android&#34;</span> <span class=\"na\">voice</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;en_US&#34;</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\t{{例句}}\n\t<span class=\"p\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"nt\">tts</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"_y-jliCa\">然后就可以了。</p><h2>然后是和电脑端兼容的教程</h2><p data-pid=\"Yul0j8h2\">继续看文档，发现可以和 AwesomeTTS兼容</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0ebe2a9ff61581fabe92653617e961e7_1440w.jpg\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1522\" data-rawheight=\"650\" data-original-token=\"v2-370894001b0119d5c0cf29299139d274\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1522\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0ebe2a9ff61581fabe92653617e961e7_r.jpg\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"fnHa1vyV\">我之前使用的是微软的TTS，所以仿照文档编写代码</p><div class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">tts</span> <span class=\"na\">service</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;sapi5com&#34;</span> <span class=\"na\">quality</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;39&#34;</span> <span class=\"na\">speed</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;0&#34;</span> <span class=\"na\">voice</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;Microsoft David Desktop&#34;</span> <span class=\"na\">volume</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;100&#34;</span> <span class=\"na\">xml</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;16&#34;</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\t<span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">tts</span> <span class=\"na\">service</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;android&#34;</span> <span class=\"na\">voice</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&#34;en_US&#34;</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n\t{{例句}}\n\t<span class=\"p\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"nt\">tts</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"p\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"nt\">tts</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span></code></pre></div><p data-pid=\"T1YY0qJ9\">然后就实现了在电脑上使用 AwesomeTTS，在手机上使用 系统/Google 的TTS服务，并且可以针对特定字段。</p><p data-pid=\"XjGOHqYZ\">注意：AwesomeTTS 官方版本已经停止更新，所以我建议使用这个版本：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//ankiweb.net/shared/info/814349176\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">AwesomeTTS (Google Cloud Text-to-Speech) [unofficial]</a><p data-pid=\"GVVpukDg\">插件安装代码：814349176</p><hr/><h2>拓展阅读</h2><p data-pid=\"RfIO0YNR\">如果想要了解如何在安卓手机上使用 TTS，看这篇</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/26006690\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-abe4f1a057875e273aa9f9670b23466a_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"465\" data-image-height=\"261\" class=\"internal\">余时行：【工具篇】TTS 妈妈再也不用担心我的软件发音</a><p data-pid=\"0VdBoJw5\">如果想要了解如何在电脑上使用 Anki 插件 AwesomeTTS 来对特定字段文字转语音，可以看这篇</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/24868747\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c819598079ea0b3bb53b8386b7fa1c19_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"900\" data-image-height=\"500\" class=\"internal\">易小猫：AwesomeTTS高级技巧之&lt;tts&gt;标签一劳永逸</a><p></p>",
